title: Deck Of Cards, "Game of Population", 1896–1900
creditline: Gift of Mrs. Dexter J. Purinton
description: Pink paper box with green label, containing forty-eight cards with maps of countries on the five continents, and one card listing other games by the Fireside Game Company.
